{"talk":{"id":29779,"name":"Ariana Curtis: Museums should honor the everyday, not just the extraordinary","description":"Who deserves to be in a museum? For too long, the answer has been \"the extraordinary\" -- those aspirational historymakers who inspire us with their successes. But those stories are limiting, says museum curator Ariana Curtis. In a visionary talk, she imagines how museums can more accurately represent history by honoring the lives of people both extraordinary and everyday, prominent and hidden -- and amplify diverse perspectives that should have always been included.","slug":"ariana_curtis_museums_should_honor_the_everyday_not_just_the_extraordinary","recorded_at":"2018-11-28 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-12-21 15:46:35","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:27:38","viewed_count":1275101,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":574,"name":"TEDWomen 2018"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/254f73de25ddfce34b0c9cb32b021dbe0a3f44f1_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/254f73de25ddfce34b0c9cb32b021dbe0a3f44f1_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/254f73de25ddfce34b0c9cb32b021dbe0a3f44f1_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/254f73de25ddfce34b0c9cb32b021dbe0a3f44f1_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a7897b789b9599b7af6c702a1d50500b4b8467e_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ArianaCurtis_2018W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6110006,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ArianaCurtis_2018W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":16888809,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ArianaCurtis_2018W-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96c